item.title: JED Logo
item.description: Utilized a mix of adobe products, Illustrator and Photoshop, to create a design and mock-ups for the JED Organization. Gave me the opportunity to create a new logo for an organization I support for free. I was also able to be exposed to a new use of photoshop, mockups. This allowed me to create professional images utilizing my newly created logo on products such as business cards, a website, etc.
